  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nThe size of |item_|[1] could be reduced after the tab is bookmarked into the default folder but before painting the RecentlyUsedFoldersComboView. |selected_index_|[2] can be equal to the size of |item_|, then the out of bounds will be triggered when GetItemAt is called[3"
